            <h3>How was The Moon created?</h3>
            It is hypothesized that the moon was created after a planet about the size of Mars impacted the earth. [<a href="https://www.space.com/19275-moon-formation.html">REF</a>]
            Debris from the impact eventually came together to form what we know as the Moon. [<a href="https://www.space.com/19275-moon-formation.html">REF</a>]
